To swap endpoints, giving i32.
Let bytes be buffer of 3 u8 filled with 0.
bytes at 0 becomes 7.
bytes at 2 becomes 9.
Let temporary be bytes at 0.
bytes at 0 becomes bytes at 2.
bytes at 2 becomes temporary.
Give (bytes at 0 as i32) plus (bytes at 2 as i32).

To main, giving i32.
Give swap endpoints.
